item.title: C-SPAN - TikTok CEO Shou Zi Chew testifies before Congress
item.description: TIKTOK SIVS TESTIFYING – ITS RELATIONSHIP TO CHINA. YOU’RE WATCHING LIVE COVERAGE ON C-SPAN 3. THIS MORNING ON CAPITOL HILL THE CEO OF TIKTOK, SHOU ZI CHEW IS TESTIFYING ON THE SOCIAL MEDIA COMPANY’S DATA SECURITY PRACTICES AND RELATIONSHIP WITH THE CHINESE GOVERNMENT. IT IS EXPECTED TO TELL LAWMAKERS THAT BANNING THE APP IN THE U.S. WOULD HURT AMERICAN BUSINESSES, AND THE ECONOMY. YOU ARE WATCHING LIVE COVERAGE HERE ON C-SPAN 3.
